modName: Wolfric- a true hero of Skyrim
summary: Changes Ulfric into a wolf, but it makes you unable to talk to him. This mod only serves as a joke, and if you're doing a Stormcloak playthrough, don't download this mod unless you don't want to do the Stormcloak quests!
